END, \"x.Category\".\"DateCreated\", \"x.Category\".\"DateModified\", \"x.Category\".\"Description\", \"x\".\"CategoryId\", \"x.Category\".\"IsDeleted\", \"x.Category\".\"Name\", \"x\".\"Content\", \"x\".\"DateCreated\" AS \"DateCreated0\", \"x\".\"DateModified\" AS \"DateModified0\", \"x\".\"Description\" AS \"Description0\", \"x\".\"Id\", \"x\".\"Image\", \"x\".\"IsDeleted\" AS \"IsDeleted0\", \"x\".\"Name\" AS \"Name0\", \"x\".\"Status\", \"x\".\"Tags\", \"x\".\"ViewCount\", \"x.Category\".\"Id\"
FROM \"Blogs\" AS \"x\"
INNER JOIN \"Categories\" AS \"x.Category\" ON \"x\".\"CategoryId\" = \"x.Category\".\"Id\"
ORDER BY \"DateCreated0\" DESC, \"x\".\"Id\", \"x.Category\".\"Id\"
